<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<opml version="2.0">
    <head>
        <title>How to Write Your Aims &amp; Objectives</title>
        <flavor>dynalist</flavor>
        <source>https://dynalist.io</source>
        <ownerName>Eckhard</ownerName>
        <ownerEmail>e.pfluegel@gmail.com</ownerEmail>
    </head>
    <body>
        <outline text="Aims versus Objectives " colorLabel="5">
            <outline text="Aims are the goals you have when you do your research."/>
            <outline text="This tends to be the direct or indirect outcomes, also in the long term."/>
            <outline text="We write the our aims in a short and succinct paragraph."/>
            <outline text="Objectives are the specific, tangible outcomes  that you are planning to achieve. "/>
            <outline text="They will be specified in form of a bulleted list. "/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="SMARTness " colorLabel="5">
            <outline text="Objectives are most effective, if they have the SMART properties:">
                <outline text="**S** -- specific,"/>
                <outline text="**M** -- measurable,"/>
                <outline text="**A** -- achievable or attainable,"/>
                <outline text="**R** -- relevant,"/>
                <outline text="**T** -- time-bound."/>
            </outline>
            <outline text="In the context of an academic thesis, your objectives will be judged against these attributes."/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="Examples " colorLabel="5">
            <outline text="Aims:">
                <outline text="__The aim of this thesis is to improve security in mobile environments, focusing on aspects of user confidentiality and privacy. Ultimately, this work could raise awareness amongst users on how to better protect themselves against cyber attacks, targeting their mobile phones and devices.__"/>
            </outline>
            <outline text="Objectives:">
                <outline text="To thoroughly review the literature on mobile security, with a focus on secure instant messaging protocols."/>
                <outline text="To analyse the threats and vulnerabilities of cloud architectures, and to recommend security controls, mitigation these."/>
                <outline text="To deploy a Blockchain architecture and to analyse the security features of the system."/>
            </outline>
        </outline>
        <outline text="Summary " colorLabel="5">
            <outline text="It is important and useful to write down your aims and objectives, and different audiences benefit from it in different ways."/>
            <outline text="We use different styles, when we present our aims and objectives."/>
            <outline text="An essential requirement is that the objectives have the SMART properties."/>
        </outline>
    </body>
</opml>
